Cape Town - A video has been making the rounds and scaring people on social media.The video was posted to Facebook by Jason Womal, a tradesman from Coppabella in Queensland, Australia.Womal explained that as he was about to head out for work when his neighbour called him over, offering to show him something cool. So we proceed to his place and he shows me this,&quot; Womal writes on Facebook. &quot;Huntsman trying to eat a mouse. The video depicts the giant spider clutching a mouse by its head with its chelicerae while it crawls up the refrigerator.A voice can be heard off screen wondering, What s he gonna do with him? Man that is so cool . IOL